name: The Beanstalk Group
overview: The Beanstalk Group, LLC operates as a brand licensing agency and consultancy. It helps its clients to license their trademarks, copyrights, and images. The companyâ€™s services include brand representation that includes development and management of strategic global licensing programs; and retail management, which consists arranging exclusive licensing partnerships with mass-marketing retailers. Its services also comprise brand consulting that includes conducting licensing feasibility studies for companies exploring licensing for the first time and providing advisory services for companies with existing licensing programs; and property acquisitions, which consists assisting manufactures in the identification and acquisition of properties. The company was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in New York, New York with additional offices in London, the United Kingdom; Dearborn, Michigan; Bentonville, Arizona; and Los Angeles, California. As per the deal announced on October 10, 2005, The Beanstalk Group, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Omnicom Group, Inc.
